Full-Stack Application Deployment on VPS (Hostinger)
React, Node.js, Express, MySQL

Prerequisites:
VPS (Ubuntu OS recommended)
Domain Name (optional but recommended)
SSH access to your VPS
Git repository with your React, Node.js, and Express project
Step-by-Step Guide:
Step 1: SSH into Your VPS
Access your VPS via SSH:
Open a terminal on your local machine and run:
bash
Copy code
ssh username@your-server-ip
Replace username with your VPS username (often root) and your-server-ip with your VPS IP address.
